Package org.spongepowered.api.text.message

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Message
    Represents an immutable instance of formatted text that can be displayed on the client.
    Message.Score
    Represents a Message displaying the current player's score in an objective.
    Message.Selector
    Represents a Message containing a selector that will be replaced by the names of the matching entities on the client.
    Message.Text
    Represents a Message containing a plain text String.
    Message.Translatable
    Represents a Message containing a Translation identifier that gets translated into the current locale on the client.
    MessageBuilder
    Represents a builder interface to create immutable Message instances.
    MessageBuilder.Score
    Represents a MessageBuilder creating immutable Message.Score instances.
    MessageBuilder.Selector
    Represents a MessageBuilder creating immutable Message.Selector instances.
    MessageBuilder.Text
    Represents a MessageBuilder creating immutable Message.Text instances.
    MessageBuilder.Translatable
    Represents a MessageBuilder creating immutable Message.Translatable instances.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Messages
    Utility class to work with and create Messages.
